    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Dahwids us Saulu: Taws Kalps ganntja fawa Tehwa Awis/ tad nahze weens Lauwu/ un weens Lahzis/ un noneffe weenu Awi no taGan-naima-Pulka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es dsinnohs tam pak-kat/ un kawu to/ un fspestiju (to Awi) no winna Rihfles. Kad wiꞥſch nu prett mann zehlehs/tad grabbu es winnu pee Bahrdes/ un fittu to/ un nokawu to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Taws Kalps irr tie labbi to Lauwu/ ka to Lahzi fawis/ ta patt buhs fchis neapgrafsibhts Wilisteris/lihdska weens no teem/ jo wiꞥſch irr tohs Karra-Pulkus ta dshwa Deewa apkaunojis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wehl fazzija Dahwids: tas KUNGS/ kas mann no ta Lauwas un no ta Lahtscha irr pe-stijs / atpestibs mann arridsan no fcha Wilistera Rohkas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Sauls us Dahwidu: Eijtad/lai tas KUNgs tew palihds. Un Sanls apgehrbe Dahwidu ar fawahin paschahm Drehbehm/ un likfe weenn war-ra Zeppuri us winna Galwu/ un aptehrpe to ar Kruhfschu-Bruxnahin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Dahwids apjohse win-na Sohbinu pahr fawahin Drehs-behm/ un fahze staigabt/ jo wiꞥſch wehl ne bija ceraddis. Un Dah-wids fazzija us Saulu: Es ne warru ta eet/ jo es ne etmu eerad-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch nehme faw Sisli fawi Rohkå/ un istaffia few peezus gluddenus Akminne no tahs Uppes/ un likke tohs eeksch to Kalliti/ kas winnam bija/ un eeksch to Kullu/ un winna Linga bija winna Rohkå : ta peegahjetas pee to Wilisteri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir tas Wilisteris staigaja eedams un klahtnahkdams pee Dahwida/un winna preekfchtur-ramu Bruknu-Neffejs winna Preekfschå.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu tas Wilisteris skattijabs/ un Dahwidu redseja/ apsinchje wiꞥſch to: Jo tas bija weens Puifs pafarkans/ un skai-stå Gihuni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas Wiliste-ris us Dahwidu: Efinu es weens Suns/ ka tu ar Sisli pee man nahzi? un tas Wilisteris lahdeja Dahwidu pee faweem Deerweim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz fazzija tas Wiliste-ris us Dahwidu: Nahzschur pee man / es dehtchu tawu Meeftuteem Putneem appafsch Debbes/ un teem Swchreem Lauka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Dahwids fazzija us to Wilisteri: Tu nahz pee man ar Sohbinu / un Schkebpu un preekfchturrainam Bruxnahm/ bet es nahku pee fow eeksch to Wahrdn ta KUNGA Zebaät/ ta Deewa to Karra-Pulkn Isra-eta/ ko tu effi apkaunejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schodeen dohs tas KUNGS tewi manna Rohkå/\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
